that it was possibly

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:06.340 align:middle line:84%
to spiritually move people
through her creative talents.

00:02:06.340 --> 00:02:08.320 align:middle line:84%
Della went on to
perform in nightclubs

00:02:08.320 --> 00:02:10.750 align:middle line:84%
