as well as her own talk show.

00:02:24.820 --> 00:02:28.270 align:middle line:84%
Della has also overcome
serious adversities,

00:02:28.270 --> 00:02:32.500 align:middle line:84%
which have brought her to
death's door more than once.

00:02:32.500 --> 00:02:35.380 align:middle line:84%
Her unwavering faith has
time and again brought

00:02:35.380 --> 00:02:38.710 align:middle line:84%
her back stronger and
more committed to making

00:02:38.710 --> 00:02:42.245 align:middle line:90%
a difference with people.

00:02:42.245 --> 00:02:43.219 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC - DELLA REESE]

00:02:43.219 --> 00:02:45.167 align:middle line:84%
>> (SINGING) I
want to thank you.

00:02:45.167 --> 00:02:48.089 align:middle line:90%
I want to thank you.

00:02:48.089 --> 00:02:50.050 align:middle line:90%
Ooo.

00:02:50.050 --> 00:02:54.800 align:middle line:10%
