00:10:59.614 --> 00:11:00.940 align:middle line:90%
I loved it!

00:11:00.940 --> 00:11:03.830 align:middle line:84%
They came one at a time,
took me over to the corner.

00:11:03.830 --> 00:11:05.030 align:middle line:90%
>> Whispering, "Ssh, ssh."

00:11:05.030 --> 00:11:08.220 align:middle line:84%
>> "What did he say we're
going to do next season?"

00:11:08.220 --> 00:11:09.440 align:middle line:90%
It was wonderful.

00:11:09.440 --> 00:11:10.370 align:middle line:90%
I loved it.

