00:11:51.170 --> 00:11:54.120 align:middle line:84%
I'm so embarrassed I don't
want people to know."

00:11:54.120 --> 00:11:54.920 align:middle line:90%
Why is that?

00:11:54.920 --> 00:11:56.170 align:middle line:90%
>> I've got a story like that.

00:11:56.170 --> 00:11:58.320 align:middle line:84%
There is a man who
works at the airport.

00:11:58.320 --> 00:12:01.550 align:middle line:90%
He's a skycap.

00:12:01.550 --> 00:12:03.660 align:middle line:90%
And he is a man's man.

00:12:03.660 --> 00:12:04.460 align:middle line:90%
>> Got it.

00:12:04.460 --> 00:12:06.950 align:middle line:90%
>> You know, he's a man's man.

00:12:06.950 --> 00:12:09.380 align:middle line:84%
