there maybe 30 years

00:12:09.380 --> 00:12:11.940 align:middle line:84%
and I've been traveling
there 30 years.

00:12:11.940 --> 00:12:14.380 align:middle line:90%
And so we are travel friends.

00:12:14.380 --> 00:12:18.430 align:middle line:84%
And he said to me, "Step
over here a minute."

00:12:18.430 --> 00:12:20.270 align:middle line:90%
I said, "OK."

00:12:20.270 --> 00:12:24.655 align:middle line:84%
