00:12:28.280 --> 00:12:30.290 align:middle line:84%
He said, "It made
me cry one day."

00:12:30.290 --> 00:12:32.536 align:middle line:84%
He said, "But don't you
dare tell anybody that."

00:12:32.536 --> 00:12:33.910 align:middle line:84%
I said, "I'll
never speak a word.

00:12:33.910 --> 00:12:37.385 align:middle line:90%
I won't tell a soul."

