00:31:21.760 --> 00:31:25.060 align:middle line:84%
>> It was in her early days
working with Mahalia Jackson

00:31:25.060 --> 00:31:30.780 align:middle line:84%
that Della first experienced
how powerful God could be.

00:31:30.780 --> 00:31:33.674 align:middle line:84%
How did the great Mahalia
Jackson inform your life?

00:31:33.674 --> 00:31:36.090 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, she taught me some
things that I did not know she

00:31:36.090 --> 00:31:39.400 align:middle line:84%
taught me until much
later in my life.

00:31:39.400 --> 00:31:40.950 align:middle line:90%
I didn't really care for her.

00:31:40.950 --> 00:31:43.470 align:middle line:90%
I went with her when I was 13.

00:31:43.470 --> 00:31:47.980 align:middle line:84%
And my mother looked her
in the eye and said to her,

00:31:47.980 --> 00:31:50.010 align:middle line:84%
"I would let my child
go with anybody,

00:31:50.010 --> 00:31:51.870 align:middle line:90%
because I have a good girl.

00:31:51.870 --> 00:31:53.670 align:middle line:90%
But I'm trusting you.

00:31:53.670 --> 00:31:56.070 align:middle line:84%
And I expect you to
bring my good girl back."

00:31:56.070 --> 00:31:58.980 align:middle line:84%
Well, Mahalia took
this to heart.

00:31:58.980 --> 00:32:02.359 align:middle line:84%
And she was worse than my
mother, who was very definite.

00:32:02.359 --> 00:32:03.900 align:middle line:84%
I don't think she
was strict, but she

00:32:03.900 --> 00:32:05.850 align:middle line:84%
was definite about what
you were going to do

00:32:05.850 --> 00:32:07.590 align:middle line:84%
and what you
weren't going to do.

00:32:07.590 --> 00:32:09.540 align:middle line:84%
And Mahalia was
worse than my mother.

00:32:09.540 --> 00:32:12.280 align:middle line:90%
So I didn't care for her at all.

00:32:12.280 --> 00:32:15.390 align:middle line:84%
But what happened-- the
thing that she taught me--

00:32:15.390 --> 00:32:17.760 align:middle line:90%
I had this note.

00:32:17.760 --> 00:32:19.680 align:middle line:90%
I could hit this high note.

00:32:19.680 --> 00:32:21.570 align:middle line:84%
And I found out I
don't know when--

00:32:21.570 --> 00:32:22.990 align:middle line:90%
don't ask me for a date--

00:32:22.990 --> 00:32:26.280 align:middle line:84%
that when you hit a high
note, people's flesh crawls.

00:32:26.280 --> 00:32:28.340 align:middle line:84%
Whether it's right on
the pitch or whatever,

00:32:28.340 --> 00:32:32.950 align:middle line:84%
a high note will make your flesh
crawl and your inner ear ring.

00:32:32.950 --> 00:32:35.550 align:middle line:84%
Now, I didn't know
these were the things,

00:32:35.550 --> 00:32:37.860 align:middle line:84%
but I knew that it did
something to people.

00:32:37.860 --> 00:32:40.320 align:middle line:84%
So when everything wasn't
going like I wanted to go,

00:32:40.320 --> 00:32:41.440 align:middle line:90%
I'd go "Ah!"

00:32:41.440 --> 00:32:42.240 align:middle line:90%
you know?

00:32:42.240 --> 00:32:44.066 align:middle line:90%
And it would work.

00:32:44.066 --> 00:32:46.750 align:middle line:90%
I found out that it worked.

00:32:46.750 --> 00:32:48.580 align:middle line:84%
So when I went to
sing with Mahalia,

00:32:48.580 --> 00:32:51.240 align:middle line:90%
I went to help this old lady.

00:32:51.240 --> 00:32:52.750 align:middle line:90%
So this was my attitude.

00:32:52.750 --> 00:32:53.550 align:middle line:90%
So I would sing.

00:32:53.550 --> 00:32:55.216 align:middle line:84%
I would sing all up
and down the aisles.

00:32:55.216 --> 00:32:56.370 align:middle line:90%
I'd climb over the pews.

00:32:56.370 --> 00:32:57.600 align:middle line:90%
I'd jump off the stage.

00:32:57.600 --> 00:32:59.190 align:middle line:90%
I was young and vigorous.

00:32:59.190 --> 00:33:03.240 align:middle line:84%
And Mahalia would say,
"Sing baby, oh, sing baby,"

00:33:03.240 --> 00:33:04.560 align:middle line:90%
and just encourage me.

00:33:04.560 --> 00:33:07.020 align:middle line:84%
Then when I would sit
down, she would not

00:33:07.020 --> 00:33:09.860 align:middle line:90%
get up out of the seat.

00:33:09.860 --> 00:33:19.097 align:middle line:84%
And she would start to moan,
"Ooh, ooh, hmm, mmm, hmm."

00:33:19.097 --> 00:33:20.680 align:middle line:84%
People are jumping
out of the balcony.

00:33:20.680 --> 00:33:22.280 align:middle line:90%
She hasn't said a word.

00:33:22.280 --> 00:33:24.150 align:middle line:90%
She ain't done nun'.

00:33:24.150 --> 00:33:25.734 align:middle line:84%
I done run all up
and down the aisles,

00:33:25.734 --> 00:33:27.608 align:middle line:84%
and jumped all over the
seats and everything.

00:33:27.608 --> 00:33:29.170 align:middle line:84%
And she's just
sitting there humming.

00:33:29.170 --> 00:33:32.030 align:middle line:84%
And everybody-- I
couldn't stand that.

00:33:32.030 --> 00:33:36.590 align:middle line:10%
How does she do that to me?

00:33:36.590 --> 00:33:38.210 align:middle line:10%
I was very upset by it.

00:33:38.210 --> 00:33:40.800 align:middle line:10%
But then I began to
watch her, you know?

00:33:40.800 --> 00:33:43.260 align:middle line:84%
And I would notice that
she played all day.

00:33:43.260 --> 00:33:46.170 align:middle line:84%
But about two hours before
the time to do the concert,

00:33:46.170 --> 00:33:49.490 align:middle line:84%
