absolutely went away.

00:33:49.490 --> 00:33:53.090 align:middle line:84%
She either went to her
room and picked up a Bible

00:33:53.090 --> 00:33:55.250 align:middle line:90%
or she just went away from us.

00:33:55.250 --> 00:33:56.459 align:middle line:90%
You know what I mean by that?

00:33:56.459 --> 00:33:57.258 align:middle line:90%
From the prayers--

00:33:57.258 --> 00:33:58.160 align:middle line:90%
>> I do.

00:33:58.160 --> 00:34:00.220 align:middle line:90%
>> She just went away, OK?

00:34:00.220 --> 00:34:03.320 align:middle line:84%
When we got to the
place, we had prayer.

00:34:03.320 --> 00:34:05.510 align:middle line:84%
We always made a
circle and had prayer.

00:34:05.510 --> 00:34:07.010 align:middle line:84%
And we said the
prayer and went back

00:34:07.010 --> 00:34:08.717 align:middle line:84%
