00:34:18.359 --> 00:34:19.159 align:middle line:90%
You see?

00:34:19.159 --> 00:34:21.830 align:middle line:84%
She taught me that the
art of communication

00:34:21.830 --> 00:34:24.930 align:middle line:90%
is from within out.

00:34:24.930 --> 00:34:25.730 align:middle line:90%
You see?

00:34:25.730 --> 00:34:29.719 align:middle line:84%
And it's that-- if I get the
